The '''Activ Business Casimcea Wind Farm''' is a proposed wind power project in [[Casimcea]], [[Tulcea County]], [[Romania]]. It will have 13 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref name="micii jucatori">{{cite web|url=http://standard.money.ro/articol_103182_12/parc_eolian_de_60_milioane_de_euro_in_tulcea.html |title=Parc eolian de 60 milioane de euro în Tulcea |date=2009-02-10 |work=standard.ro |publisher=Business Standard |language=Romanian |accessdate=2009-07-17 }}{{dead link|date=June 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> with a nominal output of around 3.46 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 45 MW of power, enough to power over 28,450 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$80 million.

