'''Pearlescent coatings''' or [[pigments]] possess [[pearlescence|optical effects]] that not only serve decorative purposes (such as cosmetics, printed products, industrial coatings, or automotive paints), but also provide important functional roles, such as [[security printing]] or [[optical filter]]s.

