The '''Stara Planina Wind Farm''' ({{lang-bg|Вятърна перка Дроб}}) is a proposed wind power project in [[Varna]], [[Bulgaria]]. It will have 30 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.sofiaecho.com/article/mountain-resorts-briefs/id_24777/catid_5 Stara Planina Wind Farm]</ref> with a nominal output of around 2 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] each that will deliver up to 60 MW of power, enough to power over 23,940 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$120 million.

